<!--- 
https://forum.shotcut.org/t/instant-flashing-arrow-using-text-filter-set/41749

Text:simple - with text opacity keyframed to turn the arrow off an on (with small fades) at regular intervals (8 frames apart);
SPR filter - so you can change the size, position and/or rotation of the arrow;
Colour Grading filter - NB the original font colour is white - however you can change the colour of the arrow by clicking around on the righ-hand colour wheel.

--->


